==English==

===Etymology===
Greek ''pharmakopoios'' preparing drugs

===Noun===
'''pharmacopeia'''
# An [[official]] or [[standard]] [[list]] of [[medicinal]] [[drug]]s, usually in a [[book]], [[together]] with [[detail]]s of their [[preparation]], [[formulation]] and [[use]].
# A [[collection]] or [[stock]] of drugs.

